List: Life is what happens when you're busy making other plans.
Author: John Lennon

List: Spread love everywhere you go. Let no one ever come to you without leaving happier.
Author: Mother Teresa

List: When you reach the end of your rope, tie a knot in it and hang on.
Author: Franklin D. Roosevelt

List: Always remember that you are absolutely unique. Just like everyone else.
Author: Margaret Mead

List: Don't judge each day by the harvest you reap but by the seeds that you plant.
Author: Robert Louis Stevenson
